---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const effectiveDate = 'June 2, 2026';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Refund Policy — Shadow Warden AI"
  description="Refund and cancellation policy for Shadow Warden AI subscriptions."
>
  <div class="pt-14" style="background:#03050f">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 lg:px-8 py-20">

      <div class="mb-10">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-5 text-[11px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase"
             style="color:#10b981;background:rgba(16,185,129,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(16,185,129,0.2)">
          Legal
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-[clamp(28px,4vw,44px)] font-black leading-tight tracking-tight mb-2" style="color:#f1f5f9">
          Refund Policy
        </h1>
        <p class="text-[13px]" style="color:#64748b">Effective date: {effectiveDate}</p>
      </div>

      <div class="prose-section space-y-8 text-[14px] leading-relaxed" style="color:#94a3b8">

        <section>
          <h2>Overview</h2>
          <p>Shadow Warden AI offers subscription plans for a digital SaaS service. All payments are processed by <strong style="color:#f1f5f9">Lemon Squeezy</strong>, our merchant of record. This policy outlines the conditions under which refunds are granted.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>14-Day Money-Back Guarantee</h2>
          <p>If you are not satisfied with your paid subscription, you may request a full refund within <strong style="color:#f1f5f9">14 days</strong> of the initial purchase date, provided:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>The request is made within 14 calendar days of the charge date.</li>
            <li>Your account has not exceeded <strong style="color:#f1f5f9">500 filtered requests</strong> during the trial period.</li>
            <li>The refund request is your first for this subscription.</li>
          </ul>
          <p>Once the usage threshold is exceeded, the refund guarantee no longer applies, as the Service has been meaningfully consumed.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>Renewals</h2>
          <p>Monthly and annual subscription renewals are <strong style="color:#f1f5f9">non-refundable</strong> once processed, except where required by applicable consumer protection law. You may cancel at any time before the next renewal date to avoid future charges.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>Annual Plans — Pro-Rata Refunds</h2>
          <p>If you cancel an annual subscription after the 14-day window, we may — at our sole discretion — issue a pro-rata refund for the remaining unused months, minus the difference between the annual discount and the equivalent monthly rate. Contact us to request a review.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>Add-ons</h2>
          <p>Add-on purchases (e.g., Secrets Vault, XAI Audit Reports) are eligible for a refund within 14 days of purchase if the add-on has not been used. Once activated and consumed (e.g., PDF reports generated, vault connectors synced), add-ons are non-refundable.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>How to Request a Refund</h2>
          <p>Email <a href="mailto:support@shadow-warden-ai.com" style="color:#10b981">support@shadow-warden-ai.com</a> with:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Your registered email address.</li>
            <li>Your Lemon Squeezy order number (found in your purchase receipt).</li>
            <li>A brief reason for the refund request.</li>
          </ul>
          <p>We aim to process all requests within <strong style="color:#f1f5f9">3 business days</strong>. Approved refunds are issued to the original payment method via Lemon Squeezy.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>Exceptions</h2>
          <p>Refunds will not be issued in the following cases:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Accounts suspended for Terms of Service violations.</li>
            <li>Requests made after the 14-day window with usage above the threshold.</li>
            <li>Duplicate purchase claims where both accounts have been used.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>Contact</h2>
          <p>Questions about this policy? Reach us at <a href="mailto:support@shadow-warden-ai.com" style="color:#10b981">support@shadow-warden-ai.com</a>.</p>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .prose-section h2 {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #f1f5f9;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    padding-bottom: 6px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  }
  .prose-section p { margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .prose-section ul {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .prose-section li { margin-bottom: 4px; }
</style>
